title: 68. What The Elite 2% Understand About Success
itunes:title: 68. What The Elite 2% Understand About Success
description: Just how committed are you to your goals? Average people like to talk about what they want and make excuses for why they're not in the position they would like to be in life. Successful people have a different approach. On today's show, Andy shares a simple secret that the most successful elite achievers understand.
